cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL 

The paper discusses a new dataset for autonomous driving, which involves computer vision (cs.CV), robotics (cs.RO), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and natural language processing (cs.CL) for data analysis and processing. Therefore, these five categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
